---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="AI Product Companies - AnswerLayer"
  description="How AI product companies use AnswerLayer to ship analytics features faster."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/customers">Customers</a> / AI Product Companies</p>
      <h1 class="mb-lg">AI Product Companies</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-sm">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <div class="persona">
        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Challenge</div>
          <p>
            Building analytics into a SaaS product. Don't want to build and maintain
            a data infrastructure layer. Need to support multiple customer databases
            without exposing raw SQL to the LLM.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Solution</div>
          <p>
            Embed AnswerLayer as the analytics backend. Each customer gets their own
            isolated semantic layer. The API returns structured data that feeds into
            your product's AI features. Multi-tenant isolation is built in.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-section">
          <div class="persona-label">Outcome</div>
          <p>
            Ship AI-powered analytics in weeks instead of months. No database
            infrastructure to maintain. Scales with your customer base.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section text-center">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <h2 class="mb-md">Ready to ship analytics faster?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-lg">
        See how AnswerLayer can power your product's AI features.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-md" style="justify-content: center;">
        <a href="https://app.getanswerlayer.com/sign-up" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@getanswerlayer.com" class="btn btn-link">Talk to Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
